{"tid":1427254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［法律撚入］許智峯：警大規模濫捕或構成‘任意逮捕’ 可能為方仲賢申人身保護令","createTime":"2019-08-07T05:30:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:16:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9dac8e7f5da217ae7c8a70852df38cebaabf71f0","tid":1427254,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"浸大學生會會長方仲賢昨晚於深水埗購買觀星筆後，遭便衣探員指他涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器而拘捕。民主黨立法會議員許智峯批評，警方濫用拘捕權力，並已與方仲賢代表律師商討，不排除向高院申請人身保護令。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯指出，近日反送中運動示威中警方出現「為拘捕而拘捕」的情況，除了方仲賢觀星筆案外，亦先後有觀塘區議員莫建成及沙田區議員黃學禮被拘捕。許智峯認為情況已發展為「大規模濫捕」，並質疑警方在沒有客觀合理犯罪嫌疑下進行拘捕，是以政治為目的，用以打壓示威活動。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯表示，今早已經與方仲賢的代表律師商討，基於《基本法》第 28 條等法律條文，研究向高等法院申請人身保護令，尋求司法機構介入釋放方仲賢。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯引述《基本法》第 28 條規定，「香港居民的人身自由不受侵犯。香港居民不受任意或非法逮捕、拘留、監禁。禁止任意或非法搜查居民的身體、剝奪或限制居民的人身自由。」又指同樣條文亦見於在本地法例《香港人權法案條例》第5條及適用於香港的《公民權利和政治權利國際公約》第 9 條。<br />\n<br />\n他亦引述《警隊條例》第 50 條，強調警員作出合法拘捕是要基於「合理地懷疑」有人作出犯罪行為，因此若偏離「合理懷疑」這客觀的成文法要求，則為「任意逮捕」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B3%BC%E8%A7%80%E6%98%9F%E7%AD%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%88%96%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B2%E8%B3%A2%E7%94%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BB%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Zybpne3YAKjwmabJhOlqIzs%3D&h=7a3bb3b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E8%25A7%2580%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25AD%2586%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%2599%25BA%25E5%25B3%25AF-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E6%25BF%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E6%2588%2596%25E7%2582%25BA%25E6%2596%25B9%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E8%25B3%25A2%25E7%2594%25B3%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BB%25A4%2F&h=3a977ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B3%BC%E8%A7%80%E6%98%9F%E7%AD%86%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E8%A8%B1%E6%99%BA%E5%B3%AF-%E8%AD%A6%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E6%BF%AB%E6%8D%95-%E6%88%96%E7%82%BA%E6%96%B9%E4%BB%B2%E8%B3%A2%E7%94%B3%E4%BA%BA%E8%BA%AB%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E4%BB%A4/</a><em></em>"},{"pid":"c49418a0656bd8999de21dccc766283656c46a39","tid":1427254,"uid":161193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:34:34.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"686e82eb88b9a337f3581e72168723be4931fc9a","tid":1427254,"uid":137309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99be0e8dc71647d566eac3b8cdce86d679d1c58e","tid":1427254,"uid":273252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:16:44.000Z","msg":"[法律人入]追究 黑警濫捕/任意拘捕/非法拘捕<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425045</a>"}]}